headline: Motorola Solutions Introduces Hybrid Cloud Call Handling Offer to Drive 911 Response Speed and Resiliency
summary: CHICAGO, June 23, 2025--Motorola Solutions (NYSE: MSI) today announced VESTA Hybrid, a new offer that unifies the power of Assist AI, advanced Radius Mapping and cyber resilience with VESTA 911 call handling software for Public Safety Answering Points (PSAPs) across the U.S.
